(187, '_transient_dash_a5a61dcab273495c31cd79aafebbdc74', '<div class="rss-widget"><ul><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''https://wordpress.org/news/2015/12/clifford/''>WordPress 4.4 “Clifford”</a> <span class="rss-date">Tháng Mười Hai 8, 2015</span><div class="rssSummary">Version 4.4 of WordPress, named “Clifford” in honor of jazz trumpeter Clifford Brown, is available for download or update in your WordPress dashboard. New features in 4.4 make your site more connected and responsive. Clifford also introduces a new default theme, Twenty Sixteen. Introducing Twenty Sixteen Our newest default theme, Twenty Sixteen, is a modern take [&hellip;]</div></li></ul></div><div class="rss-widget"><ul><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://ma.tt/2015/12/wapuus-history/''>Matt: Wapuu’s History</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://wptavern.com/new-free-hookr-plugin-displays-all-available-hooks-inside-wordpress''>WPTavern: New Free Hookr Plugin Displays All Available Hooks Inside WordPress</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://wptavern.com/john-james-jacoby-on-navigating-buddypress-identity-crisis''>WPTavern: John James Jacoby on Navigating BuddyPress’ Identity Crisis</a></li></ul></div><div class="rss-widget"><ul><li class=''dashboard-news-plugin''><span>Gói Bổ Xung Tính Năng Phổ Biến:</span> <a href=''https://wordpress.org/plugins/ml-slider/'' class=''dashboard-news-plugin-link''>Meta Slider</a>&nbsp;<span>(<a href=''plugin-install.php?tab=plugin-information&amp;plugin=ml-slider&amp;_wpnonce=ced79cd224&amp;TB_iframe=true&amp;width=600&amp;height=800'' class=''thickbox'' title=''Meta Slider''>Cài đặt</a>)</span></li></ul></div>', 'no'),
