(1285, 1, '2015-12-24 03:27:12', '2015-12-24 03:27:12', 'This post should display a <a title="Featured Images" href="http://en.support.wordpress.com/featured-images/#setting-a-featured-image" target="_blank">featured image</a>, if the theme <a title="Post Thumbnails" href="http://codex.wordpress.org/Post_Thumbnails" target="_blank">supports it</a>.\r\n\r\nNon-square images can provide some unique styling issues.\r\n\r\nThis post tests a vertical featured image.', 'Featured Image (Vertical)', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1016-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-12-24 03:27:12', '2015-12-24 03:27:12', '', 1016, 'http://ozduhoc.local/1016-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
