(1290, 1, '2015-12-24 03:52:46', '2015-12-24 03:52:46', 'We fundamentally believe that our customers are more interested in a simple, attractive, and functional WordPress theme than they are having 12 color schemes to choose from, and a fancy slider with 8 transition effects.\r\n\r\nIf you pick out a WordPress theme like you pick out drapes, you’re doing something wrong.', 'Post Format: Aside', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '559-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-12-24 03:52:46', '2015-12-24 03:52:46', '', 559, 'http://ozduhoc.local/559-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
